What is KillDrv?

KillDrv is a utility which removes a logical DOS drive. It  can
be  used to remove drives created by DumbDrv. With other  types
of  drives,  KillDrv should be used with caution.  Some  device
drivers don't expect their drives to be turned off, and so they
may get confused.



